- **Chapters 11-14**: Residential mortgage-backed securities
  - Ch 11: Mortgage instruments
  - Ch 12: Ginnie Mae, Freddie Mac, Fannie Mae pass-throughs
  - Ch 13: Collateralized mortgage obligations, stripped MBS
  - Ch 14: Nonagency MBS (including subprime)
